Ted Lewis (voice actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ted_Lewis_(voice_actor) 0 Ted Lewis (born 1969) is an American voice actor who does work for 4K Media, Central Park Media, TAJ Productions, DuArt Film and Video, and NYAV Post. Primarily, he is involved with anime dub voice work. He was also one of the script writers for Pokémon Chronicles.
